Choice Restaurant is an internal service for employees to help them decide on a lunch place.

1. Clone the repository:

   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/white-ink98/Choice_restaurant.git
   cd Choice_restaurant

2. Install the required packages:

pip install -r requirements.txt

3. Set up the database and apply migrations:

python manage.py makemigrations
python manage.py migrate

5. Create superuser:

python manage.py createsuperuser

5. Run the development server:

python manage.py runserver



The following are some of the available API endpoints. Replace http://localhost:8000 with your actual server address.

User Registration: POST /api/register/
User Login: POST /api/login/
Create Restaurant: POST /api/create-restaurant/
Create Menu: POST /api/create-menu/
Vote for Menu: POST /api/vote/
